e="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;">&nbsp;</span></strong>如何尽量避免被税？</span></strong></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;"><br></span></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;">1.每件包裹的商品尽量少于1000元。</span></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;">2.包裹里的物品尽量混装。</span></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;">3.收件地址、联系电话不要老用同一个。</span></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;">4.没有条件更换地址，那么海淘的时间就隔久一点。</span></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;"><br></span></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;">好啦~今天的内容就差不多了，不知道大家现在对海淘又了解了多少呢？海淘其实很简单，动动手指就能把国外的商品漂洋过海运到你家了~</span></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;"><br></span></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;">愿所有人都能称心如意的买到便靓正的东西！</span></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;"><br></span></p>\n<p style="cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); cursor: pointer;"></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<hr style="white-space: normal;">\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; cursor: pointer;"><span style="color: rgb(217, 150, 148); cursor: pointer;">成都的朋友</span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; cursor: pointer;"><span style="color: rgb(217, 150, 148); cursor: pointer;">快来跟M