qTXy5bf3N19lKl5aWFbsia4LibX7jwonhdHia07ibicvaxgqyTx9VwwPxYGETg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1231" style="cursor: pointer; max-width: 600px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">最值得买的就是理肤泉了，因为这里的产品基本上要比中国官网价要便宜100+</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img data-ratio="0.4788732394366197" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UkJ97umgeSJkFNj5ZnGGHItUGhNlKqTXE5IkYvRYicGp9EsVBlXMOZHmEGD6EPCdE1SRRicS4ZmENjFibluXnicV1g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="639" style="cursor: pointer; max-width: 600px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">香奶奶唇部产品在打折，可是热门色号都售罄啦 T T</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img data-ratio="0.551617873651772" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UkJ97umgeSJkFNj5ZnGGHItUGhNlKqTX7ftOyBs79N2TC8LJuPS4w7c8zeNVuicib6JGpXYKwOFWBgRWwlZ21fcQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="649" style="cursor: pointer; max-width: 600px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">但其实这里最畅销的并不是化妆品，而是药品和保健品，毕竟人家是叫药房，美妆品不过是副业啦~</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img data-ratio="0.4774869109947644" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UkJ97umgeSJkFNj5ZnGGHItUGhNlKqTXEJ3QqzkYUViawrbfw6lIn71Qhib4qSSUvw7MuqYlnGoh2P7KicJiahgdsw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="955" style="cursor: pointer; max-width: 600px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UkJ97umgeSKiafSpGq8EpIYpNIjU7ibQDsLlCNprUszTfO7a30oLxEUGTQRzxGjUibh6EWJlO3hQBE1DdL9BI23bw/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.05859375" data-w="1280"></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"></span><br></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(217, 150, 148); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">  colour pop  </span></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">邮费：美国境内免邮，国际邮费50美金包邮（不支持直邮中国）</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">邮寄方式：需要转运</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">支付方式：paypal、visa</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="color: rgb(215, 171, 169);"><span style="font-size: 15px;">戳这里买买买：</span><span style="text-decoration: underline; font-size: 15px;">https://colourpop.com</span></span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">卡泡家的产品通常打折多、更新快,还会出很实惠的套装。最近官网土豆泥眼影买二送一。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img data-ratio="0.36936170212765956" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UkJ97umgeSJkFNj5ZnGGHItUGhNlKqTXQgIon2TQFGvFhiaFPaQEAYRUYqBPhFtIhhia1TAEnIJnd8RxBicN7ruCg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1175" style="cursor: pointer; max-width: 600px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">K妹合作款，4块眼影还有三只唇釉仅需要30美金。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img data-ratio="0.8547169811320755" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UkJ97umgeSJkFNj5ZnGGHItUGhNlKqTXGutX3SQ5FNEn1KE4OaJ8YIaPVZPbWHI78qZqgmIIiaibbqYT9CogXMqw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="530" style="cursor: pointer; max-width: 600px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">推荐购买粉状眼影，因为什么奇奇怪怪的颜色都有，特别适合买几颗过过瘾，显色度也很棒。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img data-ratio="0.32199787460148777" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UkJ97umgeSJkFNj5ZnGGHItUGhNlKqTXfj8enGzoElTHz52JqNbeibaQWYQqYbPj3LUGUVWE2Dwdhv8KPEEUKsw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="941" style="cursor: pointer; max-width: 600px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">因为不支持直邮中国，所以上官网买买买需要用到转运公司。具体操作就是在地址上填写好转运公司仓库的地址。一定要按照转运公司所给的地址填写哦！</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img data-ratio="0.774390243902439" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UkJ97umgeSJkFNj5ZnGGHItUGhNlKqTXSV0y3DlBhNZPLzkjtciblRSlFLM2gqMcyXZCXc7E4a3XHBc7bFYgLpQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="656" style="cursor: pointer; max-width: 600px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">支付成功后，需要把物流单号提供给转运公司。等货物到达转运公司仓库后，再付邮费，最后货物就能转运到你的手上啦。不过不同转运公司的操作可能有所不同，妹子们要做好功课了解清楚后再进行转运操作！</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UkJ97umgeSKiafSpGq8EpIYpNIjU7ibQDsLlCNprUszTfO7a30oLxEUGTQRzxGjUibh6EWJlO3hQBE1DdL9BI23bw/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.05859375" data-w="1280"></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"></span><br></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(217, 150, 148); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">  小提醒  </span></p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(217, 150, 148); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">最后，一定要提到的就是大家最关心的“被税”问题，有些海淘网站是包税的，就是无论要收多少税都不用买方承担；也有一些海淘网站使用的快递会主动报关，我们在剁手的时候就已经预付了税费，最后到货的时候采取多退少补的方法来结算税款；最常见的就是不报关，等海关抽查。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">那么，问题来了。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); background-color: rgb(255, 172, 170);">   </span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"> </span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">我要交的税，是怎么算的？</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">应交进口关税税额=完税价格×进口关税税率</span></strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">。这里的完税价格是指海关对进口货品进行根据相关规定进行估定后的价格，而依据是《中华人民共和国进境物品完税价格表》（具体大家可以百度）。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">举个栗子：一盘眼影盘按照规定完税价格是200元，税率是60％，所以这盘眼影盘的税费是200×0.6=120.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">但是！规定是死的，人是活的，并不是每一盘眼影都是200元。所以在实际价格与规定价格相差太多的时候，就会以实际价格作为完税价格。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">化妆品、洗护品的税率是60％，鞋、包、服装这些的税率是30％。不过，关税少于50元时则予以免征。</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><strong style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); background-color: rgb(255, 172, 170);">  </span></strong><strong style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"> </span></strong>被税后该怎么办？</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">1.乖乖交税。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">2.我不想交税→退运</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><strong style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); background-color: rgb(255, 172, 170);">  </span></strong><strong style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"> </span></strong>如何尽量避免被税？</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">1.每件包裹的商品尽量少于1000元。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">2.包裹里的物品尽量混装。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">3.收件地址、联系电话不要老用同一个。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">4.没有条件更换地址，那么海淘的时间就隔久一点。</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">好啦~今天的内容就差不多了，不知道大家现在对海淘又了解了多少呢？海淘其实很简单，动动手指就能把国外的商品漂洋过海运到你家了~</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">愿所有人都能称心如意的买到便靓正的东西！</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><br></p>\n<hr style="white-space: normal;">\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><br></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(217, 150, 148);">成都的朋友</span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(217, 150, 148);">快来跟MK面基！</span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><img data-ratio="1.3570402298850575" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UkJ97umgeSL9mWrL4SJtdqBg1llkdJOOKgEfdsCWojg6PH0oVT6q0Por9Py6525Y4DHugzC9g2ClvyfibziaGx2Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1392" style="text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);"><br></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">MK亲笔签名版《活得漂亮》，优惠抢购</span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">', 'upload/20170510/1494375766559.jpg', 'upload/20170510/1494375422184.jpg', 'upload/20170510/1494375426872.jpg', 'http://yt.ieodem.com/about.php', 'njd001', 3, 1, '2017-05-25', '15544704368', '59965894', 0, '易推广告', 1, 'upload/20170510/1494375613988.jpg', '<a class="media_tool_meta meta_primary" id="js_view_source" href="##">阅读原文</a>\r\n                                <div id="js_read_area3" class="media_tool_meta tips_global meta_primary" style="display:none;">阅读 <span id="readNum3"></span>\n</div>\r\n\r\n                <span style="display:none;" class="media_tool_meta meta_primary tips_global meta_praise" id="like3">\r\n                    <i class="icon_praise_gray"></i><span class="praise_num" id="likeNum3"></span>\r\n                </span>\r\n\r\n                <a id="js_report_article3" style="display:none;" class="media_tool_meta tips_global meta_extra" href="##">投诉</a>', '1495642565281', 'admin', 'image_proxy.php?1=1&siteid=1&url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UkJ97umgeSJkFNj5ZnGGHItUGhNlKqTXJmZcQQuL78g4wGCmOZ3MH1RhJQyiaJMOzGmISickjHu8lw2iaicsLUuyeA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg', '不想买假货，还是海淘吧', 0, 1126, 59, 0, '', 0, '5', 'http://yt.ieodem.com/about.php', 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `tbl_info` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `adpic`, `adpic_one`, `adpic_two`, `adlink`, `userid`, `wcount`, `acount`, `addtime`, `telnum`, `qqnum`, `ifweizhi`, `gongzhonghao`, `ifPublicNumber`, `qrcode`, `ywyuedu`, `infoid`, `daili`, `share_pic`, `share_desc`, `is_quanping`, `adid`, `musicid`, `autoplay`, `gzurl`, `zhedie`, `qptime`, `url2`, `ispl`, `is_quanping2`, `zan`) VALUES
(5217, '今晨， 大屠杀！战争风暴眼，美国或成最大赢家！', '<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一</span><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">一声爆炸巨响之后，是满地的鲜血，以及惨不忍睹的残肢！有人流血，有人尖叫着离开。</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">22人死亡，59人受伤！</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这是今年英国第二次遭遇恐袭了！</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">今天清晨，当大多数中国人还在睡梦中时，遥远的欧洲传来一声巨响，过去一年，这种情况发生了很多次了，<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">这一次，遭受重创的是英国——曼彻斯特一座室内体育场发生爆炸。</span></strong></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.609375" data-s="300,640" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/fa3Nnz6MCNd46wS1uVPw7lNdm3ricdgPg9MxPs8fk33JjgTJa45Uf2ush6aDdVhtSo9obB0XxXKnEwFYMibJHlYw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">据外媒报道，刚刚，伊斯兰国（ISIS<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">）</span></strong>宣布为曼彻斯特的恐袭负责。</span></strong><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">又是ISIS！</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">欧洲大陆已经没有宁日了！<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(64, 118, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">二</span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">有人称此次曼彻斯特爆炸为英国版的9.11。其实，<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">比起9.11，这次曼彻斯特爆炸虽然死亡人数少得多，但暴露出来的危险更大、背后的故事更可怕！</span></strong>这次欧洲面对的，不是本拉登这种“独狼”或者家庭小作坊式恐怖组织，而是一个野心勃勃、组织强大、信仰坚定的类国家式宗教集团——ISIS!</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">ISIS，中文翻译为伊拉克和大叙利亚伊斯兰国（英语：Islamic State of Iraq and al Shams），目前控制的区域为伊拉克西北部和叙利亚东北部的大片区域。</span></strong>从面积来看，这个区域已经超过了英国本土，已不是什么疥癣之疾，而是快成为了压垮中东的最后一根稻草。<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 482.259px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.9403846153846154" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/2gHMRgK6WibQfD4fjyHgeic1yzXoBhoXwNyA64jSTd3ia2NPFxLyKSKGhianltJKc0FseZYGQ4T1q1TBro7Uk3x76w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="520" style="display: block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 520px !important;" width="520"></ul>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">本拉登等老一代恐怖主义分子很凶狠，但没有什么战略可言，成不了什么大气候，<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">但ISIS不同！他们并不仅仅是一群疯子聚在一起，而是一个有抱负、无节操、战斗力惊人的伊斯兰激进宗教团体，有着深思熟虑的信仰，有着明确宏大的战略目标。</span></strong>本•拉登把自己的恐怖活动视为建立哈里发国家的前奏，而且认为在自己的有生之年看不到这个国家。他的组织灵活性强，由分散在各地联成网络的自治小组构成。而ISIS要求拥有疆域，统治国家的是一个至上而下的结构，它的行政机构分为行政和军事两部分，疆域也分为不同省份。<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">ISIS的战略目标很明确，就是要回到曾经的黄金时代，特别是回到那个属于阿拉伯人的哈里发时代，把碎片化的阿拉伯国家整合起来，重建覆盖亚非欧、把</span></strong>地中海作为内海的阿拉伯大帝国。</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">ISIS首领巴格达迪也确实这样做了。此人是伊斯兰经学博士，坐过美国的监狱，又宣称是血统纯正的先知易卜拉欣后人，自封为哈里发，更重要的是，他宣称将会完全用逊尼派的“沙里亚法”治国（目前伊斯兰世界只有极个别国家能实现），还通过网络全世界招募伊斯兰国家的管理者，号召全球虔诚的逊尼派穆斯林加入圣战。伊斯兰世界不知道有多少年轻人被他所蛊惑，血脉喷张要为保卫伊斯兰而战，又有多少阿訇在鼓励自己的教众加入。</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">英国也是自己作死。本来，那些中东所谓的强权政治其实是压制极端宗教势力的防火墙，因为这种极端宗教势力非铁腕强权无法压制。但是，干掉萨达姆、干掉卡扎菲、搞乱叙利亚之后，欧洲在劫难逃，英国也就难以独善其身了！</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">还记得卡扎菲覆灭前绝望的呐喊吗：推翻利比亚，你们拆掉了挡在恐怖分子和欧洲之间的墙！</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">三</strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">当然，英国被袭击，欧洲被残害，更多还是被老美给坑了。</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">有个段子传的很广：<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">美国睡完了中东北非，提裤子走人了，连一百块钱都不给，还让欧洲去当爹。产前抑郁的中东北非分娩时一阵羊水栓塞，命大没死，却生出了难民和ISIS这俩熊孩子，一个管爹要奶粉钱，一个要爹上户口，欧爹稍微加以辞色拒绝，就被ISIS殴</span></strong><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">打致残住进急诊室，而美国则是在走廊抽事后烟的隔壁老王。</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">美国肇事，欧洲承乱！美国在中东问题上的最优选择是坐看中东碎片化，变成烫手山芋，然后再让经济正在复苏的欧洲接盘，把正在流向欧洲的国际资本驱赶回美国。</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">现在英国乃至欧洲最麻烦的是，本土人口不爱生孩子，穆斯林移民由于多子多福的理念，却生的飞快。</span></strong>曾经发生的伦敦骚乱，重要参与人员，就是英国穆林斯移民及其后代。根据目前的出生率和人口变化，2050年左右，欧洲面临全面伊斯兰化的处境。</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不出意外，英国乃至欧洲社会将全力抵抗，脱欧就是英国对抗穆斯林化的重要手段。<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">曼彻斯特恐袭，不仅进一步坚定英国硬脱欧的决心，而且还将诱导意大利等国家滑向脱欧的道路。欧洲的经济复苏，将更加阻力重重！</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">但是，跑得了和尚跑不了庙！就算欧盟分崩离析了，穆斯林移民仍然在，其中难免有过激派；特别是当移民难以融入主流社会而陷入贫困化、边缘化之后，矛盾将进一步激化，将成为恐怖主义的温床。</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">当恐怖主义像孙猴子钻进铁扇公主肚子里一样，钻进了欧洲社会，接下来的对抗，也许将是十分动荡甚至血腥！</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.646875" data-s="300,640" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/yl6JkZAE3SibIWkWXDV0ghZdnVrdrwTHL1UHEKjVqQZUmweKOl1yT0YLFIt3iauunJ0JPiasGMGtd41jmPib9Cn52A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" width="auto"></span></strong></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">四</strong></span></p>\n<p class="" style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果我们不带感情地冰冷地看待大国博弈，曼彻斯特爆炸，最大的赢家，是美国。</p>\n<p class="" style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">从经济看，</span></strong>美国股市这次的新高比它的历史最高点高出几乎一半。而实际流入美国股市的资金量却少得可怜。美股的泡沫比它历史上的任何时候都要大。美国人很清楚，美股随时会崩盘。<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">曼彻斯特这么一炸，等于往欧洲的鱼塘里扔了个炸弹，那些本来胆小的全球资本，还不四处逃生，刚好就进美国资本市场的大网。</span></strong>以小人之心看，老美估计心里偷着乐呢！</p>\n<p class="" style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">从地缘政治看，而正在跃跃欲试在中东挑起一场代理人战争的特朗普，这下又找到了由头！<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">美国刚好伊斯兰内部爆发教派战争可能性在增加，也门内战冲突将可能更加剧烈，由此可能引爆沙特和伊朗之间的间接甚至是直接军事冲突。</span></strong>别忘了，沙特刚刚跟美国签订大单，要在未来十年投入4600亿买军火，这显然是在为可能发生的战争做准备。<br></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">下一步中东地区格局，或也将是十</span></strong><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">分动荡甚至血腥！</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">五</strong></span></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">硝烟四起，恐怖袭击，人间地狱。。。<strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">今天，全球除了中国之外，已经没有一个大国可以称的上安全。</span></strong>我们的党、我们的政府是非常明智、也是非常对自己国民负责的，我们有效的远离国际社会上的一切冲突：联合国常任理事国除中国以外，其他国家都卷入一场或者两场军事冲突。</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">求同存异、和谐共生、大度包容、兼容并蓄，不知道西方在付出多少代价之后才能领悟这种中国智慧？从长远的格局看，中国将是维持世界和平，平衡宗教冲突的主要力量。</p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">今天，让我们共同对曼彻斯特恐怖袭击野蛮行径给予最强烈的谴责，恐怖分子永远是人类社会的公敌！今天，让我们共同为英国人民祈祷，希望他们能早日度过难关！今天，让我们也为中国人民祈祷，祝愿这片土地永远和平，没有哭泣！</span></strong></p>\n<p style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">作为中国人，我们应当珍惜今天国家的大好局面！让我们自觉做中国安定团结的促进者吧，因为，这与我们每个人、与我们可爱的孩子们息息相关！</p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">另：大量粉丝还没有养成阅读后点赞的习惯，希望大家在阅读后顺便点赞，以示鼓励！一个人长期坚持原创真的很不容易，多次想放弃。坚持是一种信仰，专注是一种态度！</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>\n<pre style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">推荐四个不错的微信公众号：</strong></p><pre class="" ng-bind-html="message.MMActualContent" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-family: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><pre class="" ng-bind-html="message.MMActualContent" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></pre><pre class="" ng-bind-html="message.MMActualContent" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: inherit; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !i