(5235, '每天用茶叶水洗脸，没想到竟然有这样的效果！', '<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section data-id="2188" class="" style="max-width: 100%; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(245, 189, 209); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="100%" style="margin-bottom: -1.85em; max-width: 100%; width: 670px; border-color: rgb(245, 189, 209); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="" data-width="100%" style="margin-top: 0.3em; max-width: 100%; width: 670px; height: 0.3em; color: rgb(155, 24, 71); border-color: rgb(255, 154, 190); background-color: rgb(245, 189, 209); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section class="" data-width="100%" style="margin-top: 0.3em; max-width: 100%; width: 670px; height: 0.3em; color: rgb(155, 24, 71); border-color: rgb(255, 154, 190); background-color: rgb(245, 189, 209); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section class="" data-width="100%" style="margin-top: 0.3em; max-width: 100%; width: 670px; height: 0.3em; color: rgb(155, 24, 71); border-color: rgb(255, 154, 190); background-color: rgb(245, 189, 209); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><section class="" style="padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; line-height: 2.3em; color: rgb(155, 24, 71); border-color: rgb(255, 154, 190); background-color: rgb(245, 189, 209); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 2.3em !important;"><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-margin-before: 0px; -webkit-margin-after: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">茶叶水的神奇功效</span></strong></span></p></section></section></section><p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 215, 213); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">去黑眼圈</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">在茶叶中，我们都知道茶叶中含有一种茶多酚的物质，这东西是有好处的，茶叶水中的茶多酚可以治疗我们的黑眼圈，还可以缓解眼部疲劳。</span></p>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/qiarxSXXLTHKfIDOtpTzshlcnSl9XQ2LXbGibbm5mVzBpicV9xOxicibkjT30urHsKpur8rTGkUFXoqmfGeMu8xfLqg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.5" data-w="608" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 215, 213); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">美白美容</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">茶叶水洗脸最关键的一点就是来美容的，在茶叶中是含有一种叶绿素的东西，是可以让肌肤变的更加美白，去除脸部色斑、是肌肤变得更加细腻有光泽。</span></p>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/qiarxSXXLTHLrbgY06u6ibpCOauXuuiawyeAHjNETG0C0E91C0icp8ZKibgHdxylzlmWibLOH6sz8Cr0o32SQSaQfyzg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.75" data-w="900" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 215, 213); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">防止皲裂</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">茶叶中的茶多酚不仅仅可以消除黑眼圈，而且对于皲裂还是有一定的好处的，用茶叶水来洗脸洗手，甚至用来洗脚洗澡都是对于人体有很多益处的，还可以防治湿疹、减轻汗脚等病症的。</span></p>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/qiarxSXXLTHJibic3em9cw8HzibVS1iaicdAKTVoePBwIcPf6PicpSibxGmj479p57GOh2oalkxESeIpV7lbwNL9NMAuFg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.5625" data-w="1280" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 215, 213); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">预防皮肤疾病</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">每天保持用茶叶水洗脸，不仅可以帮助排出体内的毒素，还可以养颜，但是一天两天是不能看出效果的，这是需要长期坚持的。</span></p>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/qiarxSXXLTHJibic3em9cw8HzibVS1iaicdAKTSPHGgpKdhYicHic2ZuDXwpjuev1UdA9fqE4Fjbfn9rpqv4fRng6VEybw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.3333333333333333" data-w="960" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 215, 213); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">祛痘</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">茶叶水之所以能去痘印是因为其中含有茶多酚。茶多酚能够阻挡紫外线和清除紫外线诱导的自由基，从而保护黑色素细胞的正常功能，抑制黑色素的形成。同时对脂质氧化产生抑制，减轻色素沉着。从而达到去痘印的目的。</span></p>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/qiarxSXXLTHJfvEvMfUUuk3Lespo6S38waXMbcMjHDwvF6wF9XlzEGcmbxGa81oGxOicAmq4aLWsyfSsbcrG3kBw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.75" data-w="1024" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<section data-id="2188" class="" style="max-width: 100%; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(145, 168, 252); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-width="100%" style="margin-bottom: -1.85em; max-width: 100%; width: 670px; border-color: rgb(145, 168, 252); color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="" data-width="100%" style="margin-top: 0.3em; max-width: 100%; width: 670px; height: 0.3em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(245, 248, 254); background-color: rgb(145, 168, 252); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section class="" data-width="100%" style="margin-top: 0.3em; max-width: 100%; width: 670px; height: 0.3em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(245, 248, 254); background-color: rgb(145, 168, 252); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section class="" data-width="100%" style="margin-top: 0.3em; max-width: 100%; width: 670px; height: 0.3em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(245, 248, 254); background-color: rgb(145, 168, 252); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><section class="" style="padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; line-height: 2.3em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgb(245, 248, 254); background-color: rgb(145, 168, 252); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 2.3em !important;"><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: inherit; -webkit-margin-before: 0px; -webkit-margin-after: 0px; border-color: rgb(145, 168, 252); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">几种常见的养颜茶</span></strong></span></p></section></section></section><p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(165, 200, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">玫瑰：</span><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">玫瑰花性微温，有活血调经、疏肝理气、平衡内分泌等功效，有帮女性通经，月经不畅的女性不妨喝一点。另外，有些女性气血不畅，血瘀气滞，脸上容易长黄斑，喝玫瑰花茶能帮助疏通气血，改善皮肤，缓解这种情况。</span></span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.624" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/eqaEib2nfHd6lIgtqyGdcY8BjoFs9yhOsFIpOtuTX2iaAHP1j86mibfOib9MZttfe3zraUgZUUaqiccaoYfiahAbXoVg/640?" data-type="jpeg" data-w="500" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 100%; height: auto;" width="auto"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(165, 200, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">菊花：</span>菊花有清热解毒、清肝明目的功效，喝菊花茶对上火引起的嗓子疼痛、咽喉发炎、牙疼有好处，还有滋润肌肤、养护头发的美容功效。</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.7513611615245009" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/eqaEib2nfHd6lIgtqyGdcY8BjoFs9yhOsxgLHN15Mice2pQURHuEtUdfKGwFjJgtzIJg0PYXibEzIUR2bdwFz7f5w/640?" data-type="jpeg" data-w="551" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 100%; height: auto;" width="auto"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(165, 200, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">山药：</span>山药被誉为补虚佳品，备受称赞。《本草纲目》明确指出：宜肾气、健脾胃、止泻痢、化痰涎、润皮毛。山药茶味甘入脾，能益气除热，长期坚持食用，能使肺脾肾三脏功能强健，还能治疗糖尿病。</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.6198347107438017" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/eqaEib2nfHd6lIgtqyGdcY8BjoFs9yhOsZzwZheteMJDwVCc9YWv8xIE1K5FL5LhKnkicesm4uDSy8nbsEhNV11g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="484" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 100%; height: auto;" width="auto"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(165, 200, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">荷叶：</span>荷叶碱具有清心火、平肝火、泻脾火、降肺火以及清热养神的功效，调解内分泌，改善人体微循环。荷叶茶能调节肠道，排出因过多的食物造成的毒素堆积，改善脸部色素沉着，焕发红润水嫩好气色。</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.654" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/eqaEib2nfHd6lIgtqyGdcY8BjoFs9yhOs5Yeg2bWCMM1zQEeJtrHAI2SD0NtbOmhII5mvcS1YiakEzeVrTH2L7RA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="500" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 100%; height: auto;" width="auto"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; widows: 2; line-height: 1.75em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(165, 200, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">莲子：</span>古人说，吃莲子能返老还童、长生不老。这一点固不可信，但关于其在养心安神、健脑益智、消除疲劳等方面的药用价值，历代医药典籍多有记载。现代