="xiumi.us" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;" class="">很多情况下我们会认为胎停育的发生类似于“优胜劣汰”，如果孕妈妈的卵泡本身状态不够好，或者形状、大小不是很好，即便有了受孕的能力，但是在胎儿发育的过程中仍然不能很好的发育，导致胎停育的情况。所以说，再次备孕一定要做好卵泡的检查，看看卵泡具体能长到多大，能不能正常排卵等。</p></section></section></section></section></section></section></a><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;"><br></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; margin-left: 16px; width: 30px; overflow: hidden; cursor: pointer;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/feB3GeeuXww7EBJ0H38FvoWo94WicgTC3yhJgZ3rJXgicfVHIdCiaP4LpyKfRUTxA8QvcW72ia2O0RTvPTLSLLSHsA/0?wx_fmt=png" style="width: 30px; margin-left: -1px; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);"></section><section class="" style="display: inline-block; padding: 3px; margin-left: 8px; cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;"><strong>2、男性精子检查</strong></p></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(192, 200, 209); padding: 10px; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;">检查男性精子的原理和女性卵泡的是一样的，男性精子质量不够优秀的情况下，受孕之后胎儿发育中也会出现一些问题的。所以，建议之前发生过胎停育的话男性也一定具体做个精子活力以及形态学的检查。</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><a style="cursor:pointer;color:#607FA6;" href="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/feB3GeeuXww7EBJ0H38FvoWo94WicgTC3gC8xicGqSdZ8vLMbS2ibVJhiazvXVVLYCJiaDEpv83uroQbFBnzCMqu5Ew/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5 edit_border" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><p style="text-align: center; cursor: pointer;" class=""><img class="img-polaroid" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/feB3GeeuXww7EBJ0H38FvoWo94WicgTC39InNianNOsdolVibh7iaqJXjMdSWGiaGUXxoWZW63UcHVgnzgMZHX4L5lg/0?wx_fmt=png" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 540px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer;" title="微信截图_20170522114554.png"></p></section></section></section></a><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; margin-left: 16px; width: 30px; overflow: hidden; cursor: pointer;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/feB3GeeuXww7EBJ0H38FvoWo94WicgTC3yhJgZ3rJXgicfVHIdCiaP4LpyKfRUTxA8QvcW72ia2O0RTvPTLSLLSHsA/0?wx_fmt=png" style="width: 30px; margin-left: -1px; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);"></section><section class="" style="display: inline-block; padding: 3px; margin-left: 8px; cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;"><strong>3、女性内分泌水平检查</strong></p></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(192, 200, 209); padding: 10px; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;">有些女性朋友发生胎停育的原因是因为内分泌水平的问题，像是黄体功能不足或者雌激素孕激素等的失调，当然，也有一些朋友因为甲状腺的因素导致胎停育，当然也算是内分泌系统的问题了。</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;"><br></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; margin-left: 16px; width: 30px; overflow: hidden; cursor: pointer;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/feB3GeeuXww7EBJ0H38FvoWo94WicgTC3yhJgZ3rJXgicfVHIdCiaP4LpyKfRUTxA8QvcW72ia2O0RTvPTLSLLSHsA/0?wx_fmt=png" style="width: 30px; margin-left: -1px; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);"></section><section class="" style="display: inline-block; padding: 3px; margin-left: 8px; cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;"><strong>4、免疫因素检查</strong></p></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(192, 200, 209); padding: 10px; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;">有些胎停育的发生时因为免疫性因素的关系，像是抗精子抗体、抗子宫内膜抗体、抗心磷脂抗体等等情况，都属于免疫性因素中可能会导致胎停育发生的因素。另外，女性朋友如果存在炎症感染的问题也是有可能会导致胎停育的。而不管是免疫性因素还是炎症因素，都需要夫妻同查同治的哦！</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><p style="text-align: center; cursor: pointer;"><img class="img-polaroid" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/feB3GeeuXww7EBJ0H38FvoWo94WicgTC3HLN7Tmvq4jdfZnyZznF2QYZ1nm3BaOHXa3fPgO5MenPgo2mSgloK7Q/0?wx_fmt=png" style="border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 540px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer;" title="微信截图_20170522114626.png"></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; cursor: pointer;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; margin-left: 16px; width: 30px; overflow: hidden; cursor: pointer;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/feB3GeeuXww7EBJ0H38FvoWo94WicgTC3yhJgZ3rJXgicfVHIdCiaP4LpyKfRUTxA8QvcW72ia2O0RTvPTLSLLSHsA/0?wx_fmt=png" style="width: 30px; margin-left: -1px; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);"></section><section class="" style="display: inline-block; padding: 3px; margin-left: 8px; cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;"><strong>5、染色体检查</strong></p></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(192, 200, 209); padding: 10px; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" powered-by="xiumi.us" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;">还有一部分朋友发生胎停育是因为染色体的问题，如果是发生过胎停育的情况下，最好能够做好染色体检查的！</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="cursor: pointer;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><section class="" style="cursor: pointer;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; cursor: pointer;"><br>当然，除了我们列举的这些检查还有许多问题也可能会导致胎停育的问题，建议具体由主治医师结合您的个人情况帮您判断是否有必要做其他检查的！<br><br>最后，祝愿大家都能顺顺当当有好孕！</p></section></section></section></section><p style="cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="text-align: center; cursor: pointer;"><img class="" height="24" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/kVOgfiap8UcmGUvzl9UEeib8R48J5cwwMHBIuzricLEeicNvhxKnvoK3MsG8smQh3SibPtTRkcjf1OswzpKZygTQvbw/0?wx_fmt=gif" style="box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; width: 65px; height: 24px; cursor: pointer;" width="65"></p>\n<section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section style="text-align: center; cursor: pointer;"><img class="" src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/kVOgfiap8UcmGUvzl9UEeib8R48J5cwwMHH5pvmMUGFDPQIgS7MJ201mXAdbI5xmxStoPoIRTc8SHiagqpIPGpMww/0?wx_fmt=png" style="box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; cursor: pointer;"></section></section><section><section style="cursor: pointer;"><section style="cursor: pointer;"><section style="text-align: center; cursor: pointer;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz/kVOgfiap8UcmGUvzl9UEe