gb(249, 110, 87);"></section><section style="width: 5em; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(158, 158, 158); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="height: 3em; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(158, 158, 158); margin-top: -0.6em; margin-left: 4.4em; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section class="" style="padding-right: 0.5em; padding-left: 0.5em; margin-top: -2.6em; margin-bottom: -2.6em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="" style="padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">不管是最早“少年十五二十时，步行夺得胡马骑”的阿克伦天选之子，还是后来“一身转战三千里，一剑曾当百万师”的热火核心，抑或是如今“试拂铁衣如雪色，聊持宝剑动星文”的三旬老汉。詹姆斯在十多年的时间里，一直都是NBA的当家球星，一直都是众多球迷的精神寄托。</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;">乔丹早就已经变成乔老板，科比也已经挂靴归田，和詹姆斯同一年进入联盟的小沃顿已经成为湖人主教练，身边的老朋友一个个的告别联盟，而詹姆斯依然在为自己的荣誉，为总冠军，为终极目标而战斗。</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;">这些所谓的纪录，其实并不重要。成吉思汗在死前曾经迷茫，究竟何为英雄。万里疆土也好，万人敌也罢，这些都只是英雄的注脚。英雄的真正定义，其实早在每个人的心里。</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;">詹姆斯，就是NBA这个时代最伟大的英雄。</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section></section></section></section></section><section class="" style="height: 3em; border-left-width: 1px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(158, 158, 158); margin-bottom: -0.6em; margin-left: 0.6em; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section class="" style="width: 5em; border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(158, 158, 158); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section class="" style="width: 6px; height: 6px; margin: 0.5em 0.4em; border-radius: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);"></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;"><br></p>\n<hr>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 0em;"><br></p>\n<section style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); text-align: center;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="display: inline-block; width: 90%; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(192, 200, 209); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">2017年5月31日，腾讯体育制作的国内首部NBA中文纪录片《一步登天》将为你揭秘一个完整的哈登，也许你会更了解那一脸胡子下的哈登是怎样一个人！<br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 76, 0);">在此之前，我们想收集你关于哈登的故事。哈登让你印象最深刻或最感动的一件事是什么？我们想听你娓娓道来。</span></p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 76, 0);">请把你的故事邮寄给我们的邮箱：997829882@qq.com。</span></p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;">我们将选取其中优秀感人的故事编号推送并邀请网友投票评选，投票第一名将获赠哈登球衣一件，第二名将获得斯伯丁篮球一个，第三名将赠送哈登手机壳一个。</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;">我们有奖品，你有故事吗？</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OQeAz51Lq7LLyKDDYSAX5Sib5c367oLZeLlrx5UIj0DRRNtNsbZHIZG22LQleGKtgo6EAK5XUSntLTHmaFBoqTQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.5625" data-w="1280"></p></section></section></section>', 'upload/20170510/1494375766559.jpg', 'upload/20170510/1494375422184.jpg', 'upload/20170510/1494375426872.jpg', 'http://yt.ieodem.com/about.php', 'jekymilo', 2, 0, '2017-05-26', '15544704368', '59965894', 7, '易推广告', 1, 'upload/20170510/1494375613988.jpg', '<a class="media_tool_meta meta_primary" id="js_view_source" href="##">阅读原文</a>\r\n                                <div id="js_read_area3" class="media_tool_meta tips_global meta_primary" style="display:none;">阅读 <span id="readNum3"></span>\n</div>\r\n\r\n                <span style="display:none;" class="media_tool_meta meta_primary tips_global meta_praise" id="like3">\r\n                    <i class="icon_praise_gray"></i><span class="praise_num" id="likeNum3"></span>\r\n                </span>\r\n\r\n                <a id="js_report_article3" style="display:none;" class="media_tool_meta tips_global meta_extra" href="##">投诉</a>', '1495731423554', 'admin', 'image_proxy.php?1=1&siteid=1&url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OQeAz51Lq7IlovqXcsOOdCqySgZh1rpZxzDf8icjtUYGEOXNZVicejSpkJRV6ibhcubFRQgHSw1pGtYYXB0kfZwqQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg', '见证传奇！东决第五场，詹皇将超越乔丹，他就是这个时代真正的英雄。', 1, 1150, 59, 0, '', 0, '5', 'http://yt.ieodem.com/about.php', 0, 0, 0);
