(5247, '在汪星人的世界里，你永远不懂它们在想什么……', '<p><img class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="0.12133333333333333" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Db87tZbia5sRB0zgl3Eibo2d8vOYRmGt1Wc3bW8fRtT3Oj1iaG6nntgDl2icpaX0ToHB0CGLhaoRxeiaSEItE6M5P6Q/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="750" width="670px" style="line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; color: rgb(53, 53, 53); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 670px !important;"><br></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p>\n<section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="" style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="" style="padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; line-height: 2; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">作为一个纯爷们，铲屎哥自小以来听得最多的一句话就是，女人的心思你不要猜！</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">可是自从养了狗以后，哥发现汪星人的世界我也看不懂啊！</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">在它们的世界里，脑回路是件你永远也别想搞清楚的事情......</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">。。。</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">一位主人表示，家里的汪拉屎的时候有个特殊的癖好。<br></span></p>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Db87tZbia5sRaibePQcSfEBKia9bFHqY5JZ1FXQrFpJNBsShibaXZOYdNW1vFOWF9an2nZmQw9yhHaqUDCPxDj7ZTw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="690"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">一定要拉到花上，而且对的特别准！<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Db87tZbia5sRaibePQcSfEBKia9bFHqY5JZrEFdcW0A1PVGFYsibu2yqCEmngS4Ij6VSBePjhIo1MOnEHnLbib7J35Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="690"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color:#444444"><span style="font-size: 15px;">主人说，不知道它怎么想的，可能觉得自己是护花屎者吧<img data-ratio="1" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Db87tZbia5sRaibePQcSfEBKia9bFHqY5JZCvEWLbvH45NmzYydpDG17WvdTHESz4wS4usibCNTUZ5nwOBUibx7EoZw/0?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="22" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; vertical-align: -6px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); ;  font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 245);" title="[摊手]" type="face"></span></span></p>\n<p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Db87tZbia5sRaibePQcSfEBKia9bFHqY5JZELyZpNu9Bhric5XMqbWZnuOSZdw1QAUib59Fnl8DT1Eq28HXLs4cUz7w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1" data-w="690"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;"></span><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">花：我说我要吃屎了吗？</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">下面这只汪的脑回路也十分特别……</span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;"><br></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">最近，一位在狗狗日托所上班的工作人员，发现所里来了一只特别爱干净的狗子。</span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">因为一般的地面它是不会坐下去的……</span><img class="" data-ratio="1" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGupxRwvCic2baZZP9FtZ3IKf7wsDIUhFjUcSHDsbvr7rHia8bMtjcdkhQ/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="22" title="[允悲]" type="face" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;"></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">就是不知道被坐在它屁股底下的那些狗会作何感想？<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.9935622317596566" data-s="300,640" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGibbicl8S8Ax6CFM5S6gpAe0ibeRXb4JZJ5KFG28iacC5iakqG05HbVSnmpA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="466" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.0066225165562914" data-s="300,640" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGvfEluArnLbHG4rzoUdZk5PuaU14NWyozgTlJaK0Is6DTicnCS3UFjZw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="453" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.9978308026030369" data-s="300,640" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGUeUKPuDlsOlRWwBicHbwSMKRVibgtibINxS3gHSUsXgAF2aOBpcHPia5XA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="461" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.9933920704845814" data-s="300,640" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGHdyp9OTeliaVTmCYOPUnUJeJsbx4gbvenVcRjDAC37Wia1nSIYgBhgFg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="454" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px; text-align: justify;  background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">看了上边两只汪后铲屎哥发现，有想法的狗砸还真不少！</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">一被说胖就减肥，可是平时比谁吃的都欢！<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="1" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGVVFwvsibPibfXYZjzSxrSMYIT0wYw0lmINVMKNWRDCTqDOqQF3FqHrng/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="270" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">主人为了防止家里的汪星人从栏杆中间偷跑出去，在它背上横着绑了一个木勺子。</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">尽管来回都被卡住，可是每天仍要尝试N次，惊人的意志力！<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="1.374074074074074" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAG2JRdXicpicib8Xpo6k25np0ICTfHNJfFy7lO4SU6mzER0wSc7NJN1pulA/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="270" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">反正当时也没多想，上去就是一爪。现在回想一下，真是勇气可嘉！<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="1.2703703703703704" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGLQnujt1yq5jRP7GnbcSdsBSmHrePfPOhqxI23XLQHlOUA6O96nxt4A/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="270" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">一早上去买早饭，经过学校的湖边发现一个石狮子</span><img class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="1" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGbOcicLS1l1INh5NiaM68ljjj9o3X2Wice3huu8NaNKUVNdLUdwbtXu9SA/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="22" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;" title="[笑哈哈]" type="face"><img class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="1" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGbOcicLS1l1INh5N