important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">网友给住在农村的奶奶家送去2只金毛，让它俩帮奶奶看家。</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">没想到这两只还挺争气，回家当天就上岗了。。<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.6980802792321117" data-s="300,640" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGPJvw1KeU0xLjEAwxTcpQYFE9DvrH19iaZRjANwPTsVwOnGzAzRDs2Vw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="573" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">严肃点，我们看家呢！<br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.7142857142857143" data-s="300,640" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Db87tZbia5sQA8jsj93bUWJLmscxS9jAGFl8Vm3kdciadMDwbETd2ejyIee8xs9ECfDOvVO2ly9qGu1Bha93y8iaw/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="567" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">看到这些狗子一本正经地发神经，真是太搞笑了</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">怎么样？</span></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 15px;">你家狗有没有做过什么脑路清奇的事情？说来让铲屎哥乐呵乐呵！</span></p>\n<span style="max-width: 100%; color: rg