(5252, '毒舌影院 | 我想用8部好片包养你整个6月', '\n\n				\n\n					<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">这件事越来越刺激了。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">可能部分毒友知道的，从今年四月开始，《毒舌电影》联合国内最顶级的点播影院，做了一系列线下观影活动。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">这是个广大毒饭开辟的自留地——这里从不放烂片，这里倡导文明观影，这里除了电影，还希望能营造一种气场，让电影和人，人和人的情感交流更热烈，持久。<br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.390625" data-s="300,640" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/J3XG34fSehDam7WicLdKPdUgkKpV7ucm2n5w7pH0XuM8pUsZ6FjjuK3c8zRY5eeEibGtngjGqO0HGKzakzOLwq8Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" style="color: rgb(255, 104, 39); font-size: 16px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">为了让大家享受好电影，《毒舌影迷会》大当家椒妹花了不少心思——Sir是从她的黑眼圈看出来的。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">比如，打造一双可以穿出五星级舒适体验的<strong>毒舌牌毛拖鞋</strong>：</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.3333333333333333" data-s="300,640" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/J3XG34fSehDam7WicLdKPdUgkKpV7ucm2Uic9rBBIDWgg9G9m5HlOA9VfR4ibQxEmOs4gHicGeJuGiaiaibFddIZEAoJA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="600" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important; cursor: pointer;"></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">有毒饭用过表示，这双看似平平无奇的毛拖鞋，穿上后，舒服得不禁让人在心里打了个冷颤，迈开腿，仿佛踏进某神秘组织门槛：</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="png" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ia17192HSYNn2oeNVLxXBCuBZKHIvDLem6lvzORibMrBP7KxTYVe33Uib9LXX2hLoq5gSjgXhzs0vgfY1K3DYibMkg/0?wx_fmt=png" data-ratio="0.9269102990033222" data-w="602" style="cursor: pointer;"></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">比如，定制一台为你点亮黑暗的<strong>毒家记忆 · 小夜灯</strong>。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.75" data-s="300,640" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/J3XG34fSehDam7WicLdKPdUgkKpV7ucm2Ob7ABLU4ib9ZWHr3aI2P2uKpOkkzmbw1nnJdozvIwAW2X1EIOWssQag/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important; cursor: pointer;"></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">虽然运输麻烦，损坏率极高，但看到那么多毒饭晒礼物，椒妹觉得一切委屈都值了。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ia17192HSYNn2oeNVLxXBCuBZKHIvDLem9JAcBFoFIp2vA7IKmKWY7XFvMIYS9yAC3qMBVaicOlUKf0LicYUEBgkA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.8994307400379506" data-w="527" style="cursor: pointer;"></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ia17192HSYNn2oeNVLxXBCuBZKHIvDLemjoQFwvlOAMkt6jQr0SKMev1OttrXFLsE7AXXK4WBGtVhaBbn8SSlNg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.4732824427480916" data-w="524" style="cursor: pointer;"></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">优化观看模式，扩大参与城市，替换一般戏院……每一期，我们都在变得更像样。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">今天，来到第三期，我们继续前进。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">针对不少毒饭提出的，预售时间太短，安排不过来。<br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66); cursor: pointer;"><strong><br></strong></span></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66); cursor: pointer;"></span></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ia17192HSYNn2oeNVLxXBCuBZKHIvDLemSlAhg1ABjhfoxOAus8g0micsTibWrqSfc8v4NfQKDcpiaNrreke7jwQ3g/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.17290322580645162" data-w="775" style="cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ia17192HSYNn2oeNVLxXBCuBZKHIvDLemQADrr7NW14zKKqfxSVQR7ShvXPcJOibMZWBaB9ibO6BKAXcQH6vZhpBQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.1979565772669221" data-w="783" style="cursor: pointer;"></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">没问题。<br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">毒舌影院将从每月月末<span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66); cursor: pointer;"><strong>，开放下个月所有观影场次的售票。</strong></span></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66); cursor: pointer;"><strong><br></strong></span></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">也就是说，只要你有看中的场次，不用放谁的鸽子，就可提前一周到一个月，宽松购票。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">除此，有毒饭反应，每次都连看两部，伤肾又伤神！能不能只看我感兴趣的那部。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">也没问题。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">今天起，毒舌影院将<span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66); cursor: pointer;"><strong>推出更灵活、自由的观影选择</strong></span>。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">也就是说，之前是一次性80块两场电影，现在可以40块购买任意一场。<strong>上半场，下半场，两场连看，随你喜欢。</strong><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">六月，毒舌影院的主题是——<span style="font-size: 20px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); cursor: pointer;"><strong>毕业季</strong></span>。<br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">六月，有最多故事发生和改变的日子。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">我们或多或少都经历过这样一个“意义非凡”的六月——</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); cursor: pointer;">考试、答辩和毕业；</span></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); cursor: pointer;">分手、别离和回忆；</span></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); cursor: pointer;">我们会嬉笑怒骂着来掩藏离别的伤感，也会泪眼朦胧中送别最爱笑的朋友……</span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; cursor: pointer;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 120, 122); font-size: 15px; cursor: pointer;"><br></span></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; cursor: pointer;"><img class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="0.3958333333333333" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/J3XG34fSehCB3ZPpT7M2n5An2t8cpzlGZdWibibuuI17cB6Kicicp3Yq7yKtmriciboJGFB2DJygpM2UgX7KEk8eQ3icg/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="480" style="width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important; cursor: pointer;"></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; cursor: pointer;"><span style="color: rgb(119, 120, 122); font-size: 15px; cursor: pointer;"><br></span></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">当下课铃最后一次敲响，我们迎来后青春的时代。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">但——#<strong>毕业季终会过去，青春期不会散场</strong>&nbsp;#。</p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; cursor: pointer;"><img class="" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-s="300,640" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/J3XG34fSehDam7WicLdKPdUgkKpV7ucm2bBITJuzicp89dIQe7EoqjNHHIRzbOcaRkZOXgDbaiaQnM81zvGCoEzYg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="504" style="width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important; cursor: pointer;"></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><img class="__bg_gif" data-ratio="0.01447178002894356" src="http://ggzr.dwjgame.cn/image_proxy2.php?1=1&amp;siteid=1&amp;url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/J3XG34fSehDam7WicLdKPdUgkKpV7ucm2kcvCIoNaWicZ3ibV0hHk0jkS4hjic5podAgJFuQrCDJiafhk117GRBM0eg/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="691" style="text-align: center; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">椒妹特意邀请“毒舌家族”影评人，从上千部毕业电影中，挑选出<strong>八部顶级作品</strong>。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;">与你再一次回眸生命最无知无畏的岁月。</p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; cursor: pointer;"><br></p>\n<p style="line-height: 25.6px; 